content.c: Here's a list of projects and software to which I contribute. * [Apache Commons Functor](http://commons.apache.org/functor) * [Jenkins TAP Plug-in](https://wiki.jenkins-ci.org/display/JENKINS/TAP+Plugin) * [Jenkins TestLink Plug-in](https://wiki.jenkins-ci.org/display/JENKINS/TestLink+Plugin) * [BioUno](http://www.biouno.org) * [Nestor](http://www.nestor-qa.org) * [Nebular pure Java Fuzzy API](http://github.com/tupilabs/nebular) * [Speak Like A Brazilian](http://www.speaklikeabrazilian.com) * [Garagem Vaga](http://www.garagemvaga.com.br) For my professional work, check out [TupiLabs](http://www.tupilabs.com) website. For Open Source and other projects take a look at [my GitHub page](http://www.github.com/kinow).
